## Reproducibility Workflow

1. Collect raw datasets
2. Clean and harmonize datasets
3. Run quantitative Stata analysis
4. Process media articles
5. Perform sentiment analysis in Orange3
6. Analyse humanitarian reports in Voyant
7. Compare findings through triangulation
8. Generate figures and tables

## Software

- Stata 19.5
- Orange3 3.40
- OpenRefine 3.10
- Voyant Tools
- YouTube Data Tools
- 4CAT

Operating System:
Windows 11
